letic-Center-3.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <\/div>\r\n        <div class=\"slide\">\r\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-000-2-1600x900.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"Angled aerial view of the Colby College brick dorms\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-000-2-1600x900.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-000-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-000-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-000-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-000-2.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <\/div>\r\n        <div class=\"slide\">\r\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1066\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-002-2-1600x1066.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"ESB worker performing electrical work in the interior of the facility\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-002-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-002-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-002-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-002-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-002-2.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <\/div>\r\n        <div class=\"slide\">\r\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1066\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-003-2-1600x1066.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"ESB worker performing electrical work on light pole on the exterior of the Colby College dorms\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-003-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-003-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-003-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-003-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Colby-College-Dorm-003-2.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>    <\/div>\r\n      <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-myrgroup-project-details\">\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n  <thead>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <th colspan=\"2\"><h2>Harold Alfond Athletics and Recreation Center and Bill and Joan Alfond Main Street Commons<\/h2><\/th>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n  <\/thead>\r\n  <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"label\">Client<\/td>\r\n      <td>Colby College<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"label\">Completion Date<\/td>\r\n      <td>June 2020<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"label\">Location<\/td>\r\n      <td>Waterville, Maine<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"label\">Completed by<\/td>\r\n      <td>E.S. Boulos Company<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n      <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table>\r\n\r\n<\/div>\n\n\n<p>As a design-assist contractor, E.S. Boulos teamed with Consigli Construction to build the 350,000 square-foot Harold Alfond Athletics and Recreation Center. E.S. Boulos crews were responsible for the electrical distribution and generator systems, lighting and controls, and the fire alarm, security, and complete teledata systems. The team used the latest building modeling information (BIM) 3D modeling software on each feature to improve production and minimize changes and field coordination.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Completed in 2020, the LEED Gold-certified center reflects environmentally sound design for the site and building, including a compact footprint, renewable energy systems, and an ecosystem-sensitive landscape with native plantings and wetland conservation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, E.S. Boulos played a key role on and off campus. To revitalize historic downtown Waterville, Colby College worked with the city and other partners to transform a four-block section of Main Street into a destination for visitors, residents, and new businesses. E.S. Boulos crews worked on a signature piece of the master plan: the new, 100,000-square-foot Bill and Joan Alfond Main Street Commons. The facility features retail and public meeting space on the first floor and houses 200 students on the upper floors. The LEED Silver-certified project was completed in 2018.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Colby College Athletics Facility - E.S. Boulos Co.\" width=\"1778\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/bhzuFt7OD_Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>As a design-assist contractor, E.S. Boulos teamed with Consigli Construction to build the 350,000 square-foot Harold Alfond Athletics and Recreation Center. E.S. Boulos crews were responsible for the electrical distribution and generator systems, lighting and controls, and the fire alarm, security, and complete teledata systems. The team used the latest building modeling information (BIM) 3D [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":851,"menu_order":0,"template":"","class_list":["post-832","project","type-project","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","type-commercial-industrial","type-epc-design-build","location-northeast-us","subsidiary-es-boulos"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/projects\/832"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/projects"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/project"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/projects\/832\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8649,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/projects\/832\/revisions\/8649"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/851"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=832"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}